# OpenSpec planning

Planning lives in **`openspec/`**, not `.ai/` or `.todos/`.

- Index: [openspec/changes/README.md](openspec/changes/README.md)
- Guide: [docs/planning.md](docs/planning.md)
- CLI: `mise exec -- openspec list` / `openspec validate --strict`

Before implementing a feature, check for an active change. Decision changes must record the chosen option in `design.md` before code lands.

Cursor: `/opsx:propose`, `/opsx:apply`, `/opsx:verify`, `/opsx:archive` (full list: [docs/planning.md](docs/planning.md)).
